# Semgrep ignore patterns

# Ignore test files with intentional security issues
**/test_*.py
**/*_test.go
**/tests/
**/testdata/

# Ignore generated code
**/pb/
**/*.pb.go
**/*_generated.go

# Ignore vendor and dependencies
vendor/
node_modules/
.venv/
venv/

# Ignore build artifacts
*.pyc
__pycache__/
*.so
*.exe

# Ignore documentation
docs/
*.md

# Ignore configuration files
*.json
*.yaml
*.yml
!.semgrep.yml
